window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>McCormick's <i>Hellfire</i>, is a mind-boggling journey through multiple dimensions, hellish rituals, urban and planetary decay, astral realms, and the destruction of an unstable world known as New Babylon. Young Lord Harrison's sojourn to the House of Adam, and the unpredictable adventures that ensue, will haunt your memory for a lifetime. </p>"; 
